    Start tracking labels, optionally tied to a command or tmux shell.

    Use this for everyday work such as starting a course/activity pair,
    correcting a late start, resuming the previous context, or launching a tool
    while the labels are active.

    \b
    Examples:
      nytid track start DD1310 lecture
      <<start command docstring examples>>
    """
    <<start command implementation>>
